description: My today´s pick was a young gipsy guy living on the outskirts of Prague. He was about to be evicted from his apartment and owing money to his father and friends. He was a different case, he had a job and was working hard, but his income just couldn´t cut his monthly expenses. He was as well very attractive and polite. That is the kind of person I like. I have decided not to be rude to him and maybe even let him enjoy what was about to come. We counted his debts, I have put the money on the table and asked him "The Question". I knew that he won´t say no. After that it was an amazing ride for me at least. He was very gifted and his body was absolutely perfect. DD60: check!
title: Debt Dandy 60
